Item 7. Management's Discussion and Analysis of Financial Condition and Results of Operations
The information contained in this section should be read in conjunction with our audited consolidated financial statements and related notes thereto appearing elsewhere in this annual report on Form 10-K. In this report, "we," "us," "our" and "GBDC 3" refer to Golub Capital BDC 3, Inc. and its consolidated subsidiaries.
